node.text: I had the best and tastiest time hosting the @Boursincheese Wow-liday Cookie Challenge which featured savory cookies created by pastry chefs who I admire so much, @lenasareini, @smallorchids, and @mirouskokovic! Watch the full video here to learn about their cookies and see who won! Then get the recipes at Boursin.com so you can make them at home!! Happy baking :) #ad

node.text: getting ready to make lox for yom kippur and revisiting my bagels and lox project from a few years ago! 🥯🐟 it took me to cordova, alaska, with @copperriversalmon on one of the best most memorable trips of my life. @spinyourstory and i made this fun video about it and you can find the full recipe here http://mynameisyeh.com/mynameisyeh/2017/9/bagels-and-blueberry-lox 🥰❤️🥯🐟 #copperriversalmon #yomkippur

node.text: growing up, my favorite meal of the day was after school snack time!! chillin with my mom and arthur the aardvark and noshing the afternoon away was the best. today i’m doing an instagram live featuring a new and improved version of one of my go-to snacks, hot pretzels and cheese made with real milk! 🥨🧀🥛 come on over and see how surprisingly easy they are to make. #sponsored by @milklife #lovewhatsreal #backtoschool (📷 @chantell_lauren, 🥨 get the full recipe on my site and see part 1 on my igtv feed!)

node.title: sesame pretzels with za’atar mozzarella sauce (part 2)

node.text:
So excited to be a part of @williamssonoma and @nokidhungry ‘s #ToolsForChange Campaign again this year! For each of these spatulas sold Williams Sonoma is going to provide up to 40 meals to kids in need. My design this year is apple themed, because in addition to this spatula, you can also get an apple scented handsoap, lotion & candle set or a hand towel set with last year's campaign design! ❤️ Get yours at the link in profile or in Williams Sonoma stores!

Shout out to all the other amazing #HungerFighters who designed for this campaign this year: @whatsgabycookin @hilaryduff @brianharthoffman @iamtabithabrown @derekhough @fitmencook @bobbyflay @tamronhall @thetinychefshow
